{
  "stem": "107.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You see, before they get into the gas chamber, not only the gold from the teeth, but everything else was taken.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So he found a way to get some glasses, and-- and became active.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And doing something was, from the psychological point of view, the most important thing to do.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And not just to sit there and wait until they get you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the 6th of March, when I was with my transport waiting to be executed, or transported to another camp-- either one, what you believe-- he was, as they were, of course very upset, my parents, to lose me.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "See, I mean I was a lifeline.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But also their most grave concern-- what really would happen is the people who were transported away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "When I came back the next day, of course they were extremely happy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It was not one day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It was two days and one night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And then the next night, in the middle of the next night, I was called back with Otto Heller, and Hans Hellman, and a few doctors and nurses that worked in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "The patients were still in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There was a second SS doctor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "His name-- first name I forgot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "His name was Klein.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "He spoke with a very Hungarian accent.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "He was a high SS [INAUDIBLE] major SS doctor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "There is an enclave in Hungary-- I don't know any more whether it exists still-- where Germans lived.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "It was called [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Seven Citizens.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I think seven citizens started it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And then it became a German colony in the middle of Hungary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But they grew up with two languages, Hungarian and German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And when the Nazis took over they threw away their Hungarian language-- not-- not the accent-- and spoke German, but ridiculously.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
